        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Modify the existing code to fetch historical stock data for all target companies (TSLA, AAPL, MSFT) over a wider date range (e.g., from 2020-01-01 to a recent date) to ensure sufficient overlap with the collected tweet data. This will involve updating the `StockBarsRequest` parameters to include multiple symbols and an extended time frame.\n"
